      "text": [
        " لِأَبِی هَارُونَ الْمَکْفُوفِ یَا أَبَا هَارُونَ إِنَّا نَأْمُرُ صِبْیَانَنَا بِتَسْبِیحِ الزَّهْرَاءِ ع کَمَا نَأْمُرُهُمْ بِالصَّلَاهِ فَالْزَمْهُ فَإِنَّهُ لَمْ یَلْزَمْهُ عَبْدٌ فَیَشْقَی."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "1.  Imam Ja’far Sadiq (a.s.) told Abu Haroon Makfuf, “O Abu Haroon! We advise our children to recite Tasbih of Zahra (s.a.) much in the same way as we do to offer Salaat. You too  recite  this  Tasbih  for  one  who  does  not  recite  it,  is unfortunate.”"
        ]
      }
    },
